===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-offer.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒfə(r)|-ɒfə(r)]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To propose something.
# To place at one's disposal.
# To [[proffer]].

