===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A proposal that has been made.
# Something put forth, bid, proffered or tendered.
# {{law}}: An invitation to enter into a binding contract communicated to another party which contains terms sufficiently definite to create an enforceable contract if the other party accepts the offer.

